 \begin{split} |\theta|&\leq\sum_{k=1}^n\begin{pmatrix}n \\k\end{pmatrix}u^k \leq\sum_{k=1}^n\frac{(nu)^k}{k!}\leq nu\sum_{k=0}^n\left(\frac{nu}{2}\right)^k \\&\leq nu\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}\left(\frac{nu}{2}\right)^k\leq\frac{nu}{1-nu/2}\leq\frac{nu}{0.995}<1.01nu. \end{split} 
